Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: nmap, whois
Description: SUB - Hacking toolkit and developer info tool
 A powerful Linux CLI tool by Subhobhai (subhobhai943).
 Includes network scanning, port checking, WHOIS lookups,
 DNS resolution, HTTP header analysis, system info,
 and developer profile information.
 .
 Install nmap and whois for full functionality:
   sudo apt install nmap whois
